com.thinkaurelius.titan.core.log

Interface ChangeState


  • public interface ChangeState
    Container interface for a set of changes against the graph caused by a particular transaction. This is passed as an argument to ChangeProcessor.process(com.thinkaurelius.titan.core.TitanTransaction, TransactionId, ChangeState) for the user to retrieve changed elements and act upon it.
    Author:
    Matthias Broecheler (me@matthiasb.com)
